title: I used the SIM tool on my Pixel 3aXL but no SIM card was in the tray. Could it have been dislodged?
content: Dropped my Pixel 3a XL with impact cover. One crack and sadly after 14 months the unit does not work.  Upon removing my sim card tray I noticed the tray was empty.  Could the SIM card become l stuck to an upper or lower layered surface inside the phone?  I cannot recall having a SIM card when I got the unit.
